channel.title: FOG mapdata
channel.description:
Someone requested this, so I thought I would release it for people who can't dump maps individually.
[url=http://up.ht/y7YZkb]Click here to download the FOG mapdata[/url]
This probably won't work without 508 objects.
Remember to pack into idx4, and yes, they're already G zipped.
